<p><strong>先来感受下热闹现场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=209456117&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200812/d11159fa0c79405d902313b89baf72f5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200812/a35db75ecd7a4ea9849c5ead820ed79b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200812/19d621adc9b64db2b60d7668cfbaae4d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200812/476d868c78a845fda1d698d8e12556a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
